item.title: How do I make a good amount of cash to start off again?
item.dc:creator: @DevilsCape DevilsCape
item.description:
@DevilsCape wrote:

try botting ^^

check this replay out

I personally use a clay bot, just makes your account continuously make clay into soft clay in falador, it's about 45k gp an hour, has no skill requirements and is very easy to set up. Only maintenance you have to do is trade it clay every 10 hours or so (depends on how much you give it, I give mine 15k each, and I have 5 running at a time, so a total of 75k clay is traded, which is around 2.4m pure profit in just 10 hours), unless you want to make them mine it too. You then trade the soft clay over to your main in exchange for more normal clay, and repeat.

Here: http://scripts.rsbuddy.com/?script=I'll+Get+You+Wet...I+Mean%2C+Your+Clay+Wet

gl
